article_title: UN Security Council to discuss Rafah strike.
sentence: The  UN  Security  Council  has  called  an  emergency  meeting  for  today  to  discuss  an  Israeli  air  strike  which  killed  dozens  of  displaced  Palestinians  in  Rafah  on  Sunday.

article_title: UN Security Council to discuss Rafah strike.
sentence: According  to  the  Hamas-run  health  ministry  at  least  45  people  were  killed  by  the  strike  on  Sunday.
